channel.title: Need help for a new server
channel.description:
Hello ya'll.. well i played a server and it has gone all crazy, so i decided to make my own server... but tho, i don't know how to code, not even basics :s but i would really like to learn java-codeing, so what i really want is someone who is willing to code my server for me :D it would really be awsome if sumbody would help codeing my server, ofc with the status of Co's i will be glad to take in more then one ... I really want to make a great server where the people who plays it has somthing to say... and not only some currupted owners are fucking the people who plays the server....
So please contact me.
msn: KevinLT_1993@live.dk Skype: Kevin_Thorup
Im most likely aviliable on Msn.
Regards Kevin aka Poya
